ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project focuses on analyzing customer churn behavior using Power BI, SQL, and Excel. The goal is to identify why customers leave a telecom service and highlight high-risk segments for better retention strategies. The dashboard transforms raw customer data into actionable business insights.

