ğŸ“Š Dashboard Pages

Overview: High-level churn KPIs and contract impact.

Customer Behavior: Service usage, payment method, and tenure analysis.

Risk Analysis: Identification of high-risk customers using charges and tenure patterns.

Customer Detail (Drillthrough): Segment-level investigation.

ğŸ” Key Insights

Month-to-month contracts show higher churn.

Customers with higher monthly charges are more likely to leave.

New customers (low tenure) have greater churn risk.

Fiber optic users churn more compared to other services.

ğŸ¯ Business Value

The dashboard helps business users understand churn drivers, segment customers effectively, and design targeted retention strategies.
